Detailed Description

============================================================================

CSL CPGMAC_SL API has common implementation for multiple SoCs along with below SoC specific implementation with the mapping as below.

  1. cpgmac_sl v0 - SOC_K2K/SOC_K2H/SOC_C6678
  2. cpgmac_sl v1 - SOC_K2E/SOC_K2L/SOC_K2G
  3. cpgmac_sl v2 - SOC_AM574x/SOC_AM572x/SOC_AM571x/SOC_DRA72X/SOC_DRA75X/SOC_DRA78X
Note
: there may not be any ip specific implementation for that soc, if it contains only cslr_* files
